          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "As we all know, many newer cars have all kinds of electronic assists which can really get in the way of feeling the road and enjoying a truly connected experience with the vehicle. For that reason, he still longs after this car. The funny thing is he could easily swoop in and buy it again with his financial might, but for whatever reason he probably won’t.",
